article.description: — Norchad Omier had 22 points and 10 rebounds as Arkansas State got past Coastal Carolina 73-66 on Saturday.
article.headline: Omier lifts Arkansas State over Coastal Carolina 73-66
article.linkText: Omier lifts Arkansas State over Coastal Carolina 73-66
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — Norchad Omier had 22 points and 10 rebounds as Arkansas State got past Coastal Carolina 73-66 on Saturday. Omier hit 10 of 13 shots from the floor for the Red Wolves (14-5, 5-2 Sun Belt Conference). Avery Felts had 13 points, while Marquis Eaton and Caleb Fields both scored 12 points. Ebrima Dibba had 16 points and eight rebounds to pace the Chanticleers (12-9, 4-5). Essam Mostafa added 12 points and 13 rebounds. Vince Cole had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ Portions of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
